      "note": "Compound local workflow over four sequential salesReports downloads with independent section errors. All four requests use Apple-supported report combinations and versions after trimmed non-empty identifier and strict YYYY-MM-DD calendar-date validation. Each decoded report is integrity-checked and limited to 64 MiB, 256 columns, 1000000 scanned rows, 10000000 scanned data cells, 100000 matched rows, and 1000000 retained cells. app_id filtering and summaries are local TSV aggregations. Monetary aggregation uses Decimal and per-unit proceeds; compatibility numeric proceeds are accompanied by exact decimal strings. The subscription section covers all version 1_3 active offer columns and exposes reported/lower-bound/suppressed-row Subscribers semantics."
    },
