          {
            "outputField": "category_filter",
            "localRole": "optionalAppliedCategoryFilterEcho"
          },
          {
            "outputField": "name_filter",
            "localRole": "optionalAppliedNameFilterEcho"
          }
        ]
      },
      "note": "Partial local readiness heuristic, not an Apple status operation. Report category and exact name are sent as Apple filters, preserved across pagination, and defensively rechecked locally. Any one instance is labeled ready even though Apple can publish late corrections and privacy thresholds can suppress data; the N+1 probe does not establish snapshot completeness. Instance granularity and processing-date filters are intentionally omitted because readiness checks for any available instance."
    },
